text: Largest mosque in Singapore.....very spacious and can accommodate around 5,500 jemaah at one time..... Alhamdulillah I have managed to visit the largest mosque and also the smallest mosque in Singapore in few days......

Masjid Darul Ghufran is a stunning and spacious mosque with a peaceful atmosphere. The interiors are beautifully designed, and the prayer halls are well-maintained. A must-visit for spiritual serenity!
Singapore largest mosque right at Tampines. Fully functional mosque with friendly volunteer and staffs.

A home for every Muslim.  Everyone has the right to come here daily and use the utilities at any time as long as it is open.
